headline.main: $1,300 for Ambucycles for London Needy Is Presented by Children of East Side

lead_paragraph: Lower East Side children became the benefactors of boys and girls in London's East End yesterday when they presented funds sufficient to purchase two motorcycle ambulances and a supply of vitamin concentrates to Miss Margaret Bondfield, former British Minister of Labor, in a ceremony at University Settlement, 184 Eldridge Street.
